headline: Visionary Marketing Executive Kristine Kobe Joins S4 Capital's Monks as EVP, Global Client Leader
summary: Monks—the global, digital-first, data-driven, unitary operating brand of S4 Capital plc—has appointed Kristine Kobe as EVP, Global Client Lead on General Motors. Kristine brings over 20 years of in-house consulting and integrated agency experience transforming global brands and marketing organizations into award-winning, results-driven industry leaders.
